  97:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     This subsection provides a set of functions allowing to initialize the USARTx or the UARTy
  98:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     in asynchronous mode.
  99:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****       (+) For the asynchronous mode the parameters below can be configured:
 100:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) Baud Rate
 101:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) Word Length
 102:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) Stop Bit
 103:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) Parity: If the parity is enabled, then the MSB bit of the data written
 104:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****              in the data register is transmitted but is changed by the parity bit.
 105:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) Hardware flow control
 106:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) Receiver/transmitter modes
 107:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) Over Sampling Method
 108:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) One-Bit Sampling Method
 109:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****       (+) For the asynchronous mode, the following advanced features can be configured as well:
 110:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) TX and/or RX pin level inversion
 111:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) data logical level inversion
 112:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) RX and TX pins swap
 113:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) RX overrun detection disabling
 114:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) DMA disabling on RX error
 115:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) MSB first on communication line
 116:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****         (++) auto Baud rate detection
