 123:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****   Depending on the frame length defined by the M1 and M0 bits (7-bit,
 124:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****   8-bit or 9-bit), the possible UART formats are listed in the
 125:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****   following table.
 126:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c **** 
 127:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     Table 1. UART frame format.
 128:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     +-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 129:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     |  M1 bit |  M0 bit |  PCE bit  |             UART frame                |
 130:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 131:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     |    0    |    0    |    0      |    | SB |    8 bit data   | STB |     |
 132:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 133:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     |    0    |    0    |    1      |    | SB | 7 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 134:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 135:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart_ex.c ****     |    0    |    1    |    0      |    | SB |    9 bit data   | STB |     |
